_sText:
This is my first attempt at a surf map.
It's a combat surf with shotguns(m3), mp5s, scouts and awps.

Problems/issues so far:
Low fps from spawn. If you have any suggestions to help/fix this please tell me.
Ramps under the shotguns are a little sticky.
The boosts after the spawn ramp are sticky sometimes or bump you off.

I'd greatly appreciate any suggestions or ideas for the map, as well as suggestions to fix certain problems.

Please download before rating!
Thanks!
